---
title: Greek Herb & Honey-Coated Cheese with Roasted Veggies
description: Enjoy the delights of the Mediterranean with this dazzling salad, featuring Greek salad cheese crusted with oregano, then coated in sticky honey, plus a hearty addition of herby roasted veggies. Once people get a whiff of this herby wonder, it’s a scramble for the biggest bowl available.
